snippet.title: DOG VIDEOS you will NOT REGRET WATCHING - Get ready to CRY WITH LAUGHTER
snippet.description:
Dogs and puppies are super funny and cute animals! They just never fail to make us laugh super hard! This funny dog compilation is a super hard TRY NOT TO LAUGH challenge! Just look how all these dogs and puppies behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
